OL,5,FLocal Pollen information for Wales
OL,7,FThe grass pollen season for Wales can
OL,8,Fvary quite a lot over a short
OL,9,Fdistance. Although generally it can be
OL,10,Fsevere in the south and towards the
OL,11,FWelsh-English border, elsewhere Wales
OL,12,Ftypically experiences a mild grass
OL,13,Fpollen.
OL,15,FLower Pollen Count AreasJThe wind
OL,16,Fdirection in the UK is predominantly
OL,17,Fsouthwesterly and therefore coastal
OL,18,Fareas are less susceptible high pollen
OL,19,Flevels.
